BTCSERV.net was a free for all [[Mining Pool|Pooled_Mining]] with proportional [[Bitcoin]] payouts located in Germany. The pool was launched on July 9th, 2011 and it featured

* [[Long_Polling]]
* SSL encrypted user interface
* Fast payouts

Only the [[transaction fees|transaction_fees]] were kept by the pool operator.

In feburary of 2012 the pool got hacked and 400BTC was stolen, since than it has been offline.

